Package stratpoint.samuelnieva

Class Book

java.lang.Object
stratpoint.samuelnieva.Book
Direct Known Subclasses:
Biography, Manga, Novel
public class Book extends Object
The Book class. This is the template for the Book subclasses: Biography, Novel and Manga. It contains the attributes common to all three, as well as the template for the outputInfo method which displays the information of the Book through STDOUT.
